    <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="C:\Users\sharmabi\git\documentation\helion\swift\allocating_disk_drives.dita" xtrc="p:1;6:8">The disk model describes the configuration of disk drives
      <!--number of disk present on a particular server--> and its
